title: Motley Fool Money:  10.09.2009
description: Retailers report better than expected same-store sales numbers. Dr. Doom warns that it could get worse. Dell and Google take on the iPhone. And Google and Microsoft court Twitter. We'll tackle those topics, talk about McDonald’s new artsy side, and share three stock ideas.
